author: jleroux
msg: A patch from BJ Freeman "Datafile does not catch lack of delimiter if at end of line." (https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-3026) - OFBIZ-3026
There was an issue if the datafile did not have the last delimiter before the CRLF.  This fixes it when there are not data for a field and also fixes the EOL.
